{"tid":1453998,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅色治安風險警告現正生效","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T01:28:15.000Z","uid":222614,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fc13cfaebe99cabb56e10895507de5975fa50e91","tid":1453998,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:53:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><ins>紅色治安風險警告現正生效</ins></div></span><br />\n<br />\n由於有警察參與破壞社會治安之事，肆意攻擊市民，現時治安風險大為提高。<br />\n<br />\n現時社會治安只靠部份市民自發去維持，無故受襲風險大為提高，<span style=\"color: red;\">建議市民外出前適量配備武裝</span>以作防衛之用。<br />\n<br />\n紅色治安風險警告表示，當罪案或意外發生時，警方無能力向受影響人士提供迅速協助及對緊急求助作出即時回應，因此，市民之人身安全及財產現已無法得到保障。<br />\n<br />\n更甚者，已有警察參與破壞社會治安之事，無故襲擊及傷害市民。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警告！罪案發生風險極高</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警告！香港警察已無法維持治安</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警告！市民受襲風險極高</span></span><br />\n<br />\n市民若要外出，應配備適量武裝保護自己<br />\n<br />\n注意！每人都有權行使「公民逮捕」，呼籲市民當身邊有罪案發生時挺身而出，保護弱勢。"},{"pid":"196bce628557ff3662d2263bfb4fa780d3d6fc80","tid":1453998,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:16:48.000Z","msg":"toei"},{"pid":"fa6809de53e5f9f19c5cadce7fe984f3eb7e17c0","tid":1453998,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:18:56.000Z","msg":"警告發出日期：2019年8月12日 01:53:40<br />\n<br />\n7 日後既今日就發生將軍澳斬人事件"},{"pid":"767ddf77aaf461f3147e7366a5e323b5336a43a6","tid":1453998,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:19:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fb8583bbde4d6b4463679da24034ad5b1d4bdf85","tid":1453998,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:19:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"51c99385e14fe77866bf343b86a1bc6a63c5e5c5","tid":1453998,"uid":222614,"like":0